          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Presidential Allowance Modernization Act</strong></p> <p>Revises provisions relating to presidential pensions to&nbsp;allow former&nbsp;Presidents&nbsp;an annuity&nbsp;of $200,000&nbsp;and an additional monetary&nbsp;allowance&nbsp;of $200,000 per year. Reduces such pension by the amount that a President's adjusted gross income in a taxable year exceeds $400,000.&nbsp; </p> <p>Increases from $20,000 to $100,000 the annual annuity of a surviving spouse of a former President. </p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2015-04-14T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
